  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a kettle</p><p>Chop your <strong>sweet potato[es]</strong> (skins on) into large, bite-sized pieces, then add to a pot of plenty of <strong>boiled water </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, cook for 12-15 min or until fork-tender, then drain and return to the pot</p>",
