      "instruction": "<p>Pat your <strong>haddock bites</strong> dry with kitchen paper,<strong> </strong>then<strong> </strong>add them to a bowl with your <strong>curry powder</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Tip: Unevenly sized haddock bites? Chop any larger ones into bite-sized pieces!</p><p>Give everything a good mix up until the haddock is fully coated</p>",
