    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> panko breadcrumbs </strong>to a plate</p><p>Run the<strong> drained sweet potato</strong> under <strong>cold running water</strong> until cool enough to handle, then return to the pot and mash until smooth</p><p>Add the <strong>flaked haddock</strong> to the crushed sweet potato with a good pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>, then mix gently</p><p>Divide the mix and shape into 2 fish cakes per person, then press into the <strong>panko breadcrumbs </strong>firmly to evenly coat</p>",
