    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Top, tail and slice your <strong>radishes</strong> (as finely as you can)</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>grated carrot</strong>, <strong>sliced radishes</strong> and <strong>sliced spring onion </strong>to<strong> </strong>a bowl with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, <strong>half</strong> your <strong>nigella seeds </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong> and a pinch<strong> </strong>of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your <strong>tangy</strong> <strong>slaw</strong></p>",
