      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>curried</strong> <strong>haddock fish cakes</strong> with the <strong>tangy</strong> <strong>slaw</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle some of the<strong> mango mayo</strong> over the fish cakes and serve the rest to the side for dipping</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
